      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 2019: loadMissingBodyOverwrites only processes messages already present in loadedHistory_.quickAccess, but it does not update the messages vector that was just returned by loadMessages. Even if ConversationModule calls this before SwarmLoaded, the emitted payload will still be stale unless it is rebuilt from loadedHistory_ after injection or the transformation is performed directly on the result vector. Consider returning transformed copies from this method and emitting those.",
