      "writtenOn": "2026-06-03T14:44:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Line 2053: Messages for which a plugin does not produce bodyOverwrite are treated as missing forever. Every future load/reload will re-run plugin transformations for the same messages and editions, which can become expensive on large conversations and may repeatedly invoke external plugin work. Store an explicit processed/empty marker or track a generation/version so unchanged messages are not transformed repeatedly when no overwrite is produced.",
